'''Idurar n Anden''' neɣ '''Andes''' d [[azrar n idurar]] ɣeziffen, Yeččuṛen d [[afarnu|ifarnuyen]], yezga-d deg umalu n [[Tamrikt n Wenẓul|Temrikt n Wenẓul]], azal n teɣezi-ynes yessaweṭ ar 8000 n yikilumtren seg [[Venezuela]] arma d [[tigzirt]] n [[Akal n Tmes|Wakal n Tmes]]. D tehri n 500 km, Akken daɣen illan-t tqacucin ugarent 5000 m di teflel

Adrar iflalen (iɛlayen) akk deg wezrar n Anden d taqacuct n [[Aconcagua]] s teflel n 6.959 n imitren  

== Imezdaɣ ==
Azal ameqran n wid yettidiren deg idurar n Anden d [[Imezdaɣ iẓaṛanen n Marikan]], ddren deg yegnan iflalen ay d-yezgan gar idurar-nni seg [[tkerrazt]] (tfellaḥt) yerna [[Tujjwa|ssajjawen]] kra seg [[afares|yifarisen-nsen]] am [[Taneɣlust|Tneɣlust]], am akken ay ddren daɣen seg [[Takessawt|tkessawt]]. 

== Akal d iylan ==

[[Akal]] n idurar-a n Anden ur [[Taylullest n wakal|ylullesn ara]], Maca yeččuṛ d [[amɣuz|imɣuzen]] yerna llan waṭas n telmas n yemɣuzen am [[iɣir]], [[uzzal]] akk d  [[Afitṛul]] 

